      interactive map filled with local eateries, each offering unique flavors
      and stories waiting to be uncovered. Every corner you explore brings new
      opportunities to learn about the neighborhoodâ€™s food culture and hidden
      gems.
    </Section>
    <Section
      title="VISIT"
      image="/images/visit.webp"
      hasButton={false}
      background="var(--bun-2)"
      >Step inside eateries through your screen, virtually exploring their
      menus, atmospheres, and signature dishes. Experience the sights and
      stories of each place as if you were there in person, all while collecting
      insights and discovering what makes every eatery unique.
    </Section>
    <Section
      title="COLLECT"
      image="/images/collect.webp"
      hasButton={false}
      order="-1"
      >Track your progress and celebrate your achievements as you unlock badges,
      discover new dishes, and complete challenges along the way. Each visit,
      each dish tried, and each connection made adds to your collection, turning
      experiences into a fun and interactive journey that helps supporting local
      eateries.
    </Section>
    <Section
      title="CONNECT"
      image="/images/connect.webp"
      hasButton={false}
